    Data:    We may process Identity Data, Device/Network Data, Usage Information, and Contact Data in connection with marketing communications (such as emails), which you might receive if you register for an account, choose to receive marketing communications, or engage in a transaction allowing us to send you those marketing communications. We may also collect Device/Network Data when you open or interact with those marketing communications.
